TextEng: Who are you?
I'd like to ask you some questions.
Text: 몇 가지 물어보고 싶은 게 있어.

TextEng: Who you be?
Me want ask questions.
Goodbye.
Do you know what's going on in Luskan?
Text: 러스칸에서 무슨 일이 일어나고 있는지 알아?

TextEng: I'm looking for work, if you know of any.
I need some directions.
You know stuff 'bout Luskan?
Me look for job. You got one?
Me need directions.
What problem is that?
What is little problem?
Tell me about the job.
You tells me 'bout job.
Why does he want the baby?
I can't just take the baby from her father, either.
You think you could be a proper mother?
Text: 네가 제대로 된 엄마가 될 수 있을 것 같아?

TextEng: I could help you.
Why he wants baby?
Me no want take baby from father, either.
You think you could be a proper mother?
Text: 너... 좋은 엄마 될 수 있어?

TextEng: Me coulds help you.
I have some more questions about this job.
Text: 이 일에 대해 더 물어볼 게 있어.

TextEng: Any chance I could get an advance on this?
Me got some questions 'bout job.
Text: 나... 일에 대해 더 물어볼 거 있어.

TextEng: Me want money up front to do this.
Why does he want the baby?
I can't just take the baby from her father, either.
You think you could be a proper mother?
Text: 네가 제대로 된 엄마가 될 수 있을 것 같아?

TextEng: Is there anything else about this job you're not telling me?
Text: 이 일에 대해 말 안 한 게 더 있어?

TextEng: Why he wants baby?
Me no want take baby from father, either.
You think you could be a proper mother?
Text: 너... 좋은 엄마 될 수 있어?

TextEng: There be more stuff 'bout job you not tell me?
Text: 일에 대해... 더 안 말한 거 있어?

TextEng: I want to ask you again about getting your baby for you.
Text: 아기를 찾아다 주는 일에 대해 다시 물어보고 싶어.

TextEng: Me want ask you again 'bout getting your baby for you.
Text: 나... 아기 찾는 일 다시 물어볼래.

TextEng: You mentioned something about a job before.
You was talking 'bout job before.
I have your baby with me.
Me gots baby here.
You're one of the brothel girls, then?
You brothel girl, huh?
What's the problem?
What problem?
You don't seem like the type.
Text: 그런 일을 할 것 같아 보이진 않는데.

TextEng: You not looks like you belongs here.
Text: 너... 여기 어울리는 것 같진 않아.

TextEng: So? I want to hire you anyway.
So? Me wants to hire you still.
No, I don't want to get involved.
No, me not wants to be involved.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> It wasn't an easy task. Don't you think a bit more would be suitable?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 쉬운 일이 아니었어. 좀 더 줘야 하는 거 아닌가?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me work hard for this. You give more gold, yes?
No it's not. Give me all of it or the kid dies, girl.
Text: 아니 충분하지 않아. 다 내놔. 안 그러면 애가 죽어.

TextEng: No it not enough. Give all or baby dies!
Text: 아니... 부족해. 다 줘. 안 그러면 아기 죽어!

TextEng: Is that all? I guess I'll take the baby back to Galrone.
Text: 그게 다야? 그럼 아기를 갈론에게 다시 데려가야겠군.

TextEng: Is all? Okays, me takes baby to Galrone again.
Text: 그게 다야? 알았어... 나 아기 갈론한테 다시 데려갈게.

TextEng: Keep your gold for the baby. It was my pleasure.
Text: 돈은 아기를 위해 써. 기꺼이 한 일이야.

TextEng: Keeps gold for baby. Me not wants it.
Text: 돈... 아기한테 써. 나 필요 없어.

TextEng: That would be fine.
Me okay with that.
No. I guess I'll take the baby back to Galrone.
No. Me takes baby to Galrone again.
Text: 싫어. 나 아기 갈론한테 다시 데려갈래.

TextEng: I suppose it will have to do.
Me guess it okay, then.
You're right. The original reward will do.
Text: 네 말이 맞아. 원래 보수로 하지.

TextEng: You right. Reward is okay.
Text: 네 말 맞아. 원래 보수로 할게.

TextEng: No, no, keep the gold.
No, you keeps gold.
I am sure. In fact, I have 250 gp. Take it and be safe.
Text: 정말이야. 사실 250 금화가 있어. 받아서 안전하게 지내.

TextEng: Me sure. Here... 250 gp. Take and be safe.
Text: 진짜야. 여기... 250 금화. 받아서 안전하게 있어.
